2025-10-13T12:55:06: Velocity area station located approximately 180m upstream of Pultney Weir, Bath.
Gauged daily flow record discontinued October 1969.
Surface geology comprising of clays, limestones, sandstones, conglomerates and other rocks. Land use is mostly rural but with some urban areas.
Flows affected by abstractions for public water supply, groundwater abstractions/recharge and effluent returns.
